  "synopsis": "When I woke up, I had reincarnated into the world of a game I played in my past life. And what's more, as a monster that's hostile to humanity! It couldn't be helped, so I just lived quietly so humans wouldn't find me, but... \n\nThe heroine, Noa, who was my oshi in my past life, had collapsed near my home!! \n\nAfter I protected and nursed her, my oshi gave me the name \"Rei\", so I decided to follow and protect Noa as my oshi for life. I meet other characters from the game too, and I'm watching over Noa's growth, but... the real Noa seems to be the type who's a bit clingy and has a... \"heavy\" love? \n\nThis is the story of me, reincarnated as a monster, somehow overcoming hardships together with my beloved oshi. \n\n(Source: Kadokawa, translated)",
